My guess would be digestive tract problems. Yogurt is awesome for that. You can also try not to eat anything unnatural, like fast food or anything. Eat healthy, and drink lots of water. I get this often when I get too busy to eat healthy meals and eat crap for a week.

Either way I think you should go and see your GP before planning on going away.
It could be nothing but then again it could be something and I'm sure you don't want to go away and while away your condition get's worse.
